{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420820/extras/SteamCustomDescription.png?t=1691087812\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Overview</h2>Welcome to Vae Victis, the minimalistic turn-based strategy game where you choose your faction, build your army, and crush your enemies to expand your empire. With intuitive turn-based combat, this game is easy to pick up but hard to master. Quickly form defensive lines and rapidly attack to claim victory!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420820/extras/vaegif.gif?t=1691087812\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Campaign</h2>Start as a small kingdom and work to build a successful empire. Expand your borders while keeping a close eye on your enemies, who are always looking for an opportunity to strike. But war is not your only challenge; managing your economy and people is key to your success.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Multiplayer</h2>Go head-to-head with your friends in custom battles and surprise them with your cunning Celtic archers, strong Roman swordsmen, or Hunnic cavalry maneuvers.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Custom Battles</h2>Not in the mood for a full campaign? Start a custom battle, set your army and enemies, and deploy your strategy for a quick, intense battle.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Intuitive Turn-Based Combat</strong><br>Most turn-based combat systems are slow and clunky, however in Vae Victis the combat is fast and dynamic. Quickly form defensive lines and rapidly attack!<br><br></li><li><strong>Factions</strong><br>Choose from a variety of factions with their own special abilities and units to provide a twist to your strategy!<br><br></li><li><strong>Units</strong><br>All units are created to fit their faction, with buffs and nerfs based on the factions' abilities. Making each battle unique.<br><br></li><li><strong>Dynamic Combat</strong><br>Battle outcomes take into account a myriad of factors from unit position, to unit health to special abilities making each situation unique.<br><br><i>woe to the conquered</i></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Start the game","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2420820/09b5d3b52a0c94e87b12b0584eb06910b8e44842.jpg"},{"name":"Winner Winner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2420820/09b5d3b52a0c94e87b12b0584eb06910b8e44842.jpg"},{"name":"Big Fat Loser","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2420820/09b5d3b52a0c94e87b12b0584eb06910b8e44842.jpg"},{"name":"Start Your Campaign","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2420820/09b5d3b52a0c94e87b12b0584eb06910b8e44842.jpg"},{"name":"You Suck","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2420820/09b5d3b52a0c94e87b12b0584eb06910b8e44842.jpg"},{"name":"Vae Victis","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2420820/09b5d3b52a0c94e87b12b0584eb06910b8e44842.jpg"},{"name":"Bottom Frag","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2420820/09b5d3b52a0c94e87b12b0584eb06910b8e44842.jpg"},{"name":"Cheeser","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2420820/09b5d3b52a0c94e87b12b0584eb06910b8e44842.jpg"},{"name":"Goof Crew","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2420820/09b5d3b52a0c94e87b12b0584eb06910b8e44842.jpg"},{"name":"Veni Vidi Vici","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2420820/09b5d3b52a0c94e87b12b0584eb06910b8e44842.jpg"}],"total":14},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420820/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1691087812","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420820/page_bg_genera